  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "I've run into some limitations I believe are complete blockers for external system development using the JSON-RPC interface, there are work arounds but they are needlessly complex and fragile.\n- no method of creating an account keypair (except from the command line)\n- no method unlocking an account keypair (except from the command line)\n- no method of notifying an external application of changes such as\n  - new block\n  - account event \n",
